20#ifndef GCC_RTL_CHKP_H
21#define GCC_RTL_CHKP_H
22
23#define DECL_BOUNDS_RTL(NODE) (chkp_get_rtl_bounds (DECL_WRTL_CHECK (NODE)))
24
25#define SET_DECL_BOUNDS_RTL(NODE, VAL) \
26 (chkp_set_rtl_bounds (DECL_WRTL_CHECK (NODE), VAL))
27
28extern rtx chkp_get_rtl_bounds (tree node);
29extern void chkp_set_rtl_bounds (tree node, rtx val);
30extern void chkp_reset_rtl_bounds ();
31extern void chkp_split_slot (rtx slot, rtx *slot_val, rtx *slot_bnd);
32extern rtx chkp_join_splitted_slot (rtx val, rtx bnd);
33extern rtx chkp_get_value_with_offs (rtx par, rtx offs);
34extern void chkp_copy_bounds_for_stack_parm (rtx slot, rtx value, tree type);
35extern void chkp_emit_bounds_store (rtx bounds, rtx value, rtx mem);
36extern void chkp_put_regs_to_expr_list (rtx par);
37
38#endif /* GCC_RTL_CHKP_H */
